<br/>
<div class="jumbotron">
  <h1>Blocitoff</h1>
  <p>Blocitoff made it simple to track your daily to-do items</p>
  <p>
    <% if current_user %>
      <%= link_to "Sign Out", destroy_user_session_path, method: :delete, class: 'btn btn-primary' %>
    <% if current_user.list == nil %>
           <%= link_to "New To-do List", new_list_path, class: 'btn btn-success' %>
        <%else%>
      <%= link_to current_user.list.title, list_path(current_user.list.id), class: 'btn btn-primary' %>
        <%end%>
    <%else%>
    <%= link_to "Sign In", new_user_session_path, class: 'btn btn-primary' %> or
      <%= link_to "Sign Up", new_user_registration_path, class: 'btn btn-primary' %> today!
    <%end%>
  </p>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <h2>Access from any where!</h2>
    <p>Blocitoff will keep all your tasks in one place.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <h2>It's all about dead lines</h2>
    <p>Blocitoff will track your dead lines.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <h2>Put your dreams in a list!</h2>
    <p>Blocitoff can be used to update your bucket list .</p>
  </div>
</div>

